        output='# Matching 模块实现\n\n## 职责\n\n负责推荐卡片生成、滑动操作处理
、双向匹配判定与通知。\n\n## 流程图\n\n### 推荐卡片\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagr
am\n    participant C as Flutter App\n    participant API as MatchingController\
n    participant S as MatchingService\n    participant DB as MySQL\n    particip
ant R as Redis\n\n    C->>API: GET /matching/recommendations\n    API->>S: getRe
commendations(userId, location, filters)\n    S->>R: get candidate pool\n    alt
cache miss\n        S->>DB: query candidates (Haversine + filters)\n        DB--
>>S: user list\n        S->>R: cache candidate pool (TTL 5min)\n    end\n    S--
>>API: sorted cards\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\n```\n\n### 滑动与匹配\n\n```mermaid\n
sequenceDiagram\n    participant C as Flutter App\n    participant API as Matchi
ngController\n    participant S as MatchingService\n    participant DB as MySQL\
n    participant WS as Socket.io\n\n    C->>API: POST /matching/actions (target_
id, action=like)\n    API->>S: recordAction(userId, targetId, action)\n    S->>D
B: insert match_actions\n    S->>DB: checkMutualLike(targetId, userId)\n    alt 
mutual like\n        S->>DB: create match + conversation\n        S->>WS: emit m
atch:created to both users\n    end\n    S-->>API: result\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\
n```\n\n## 关键文件\n\n| 文件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| Controller | `apps/ap
i/src/modules/matching/matching.controller.ts` |\n| Service | `apps/api/src/modu
les/matching/matching.service.ts` |\n| DTO | `apps/api/src/modules/matching/dto/
` |\n| Flutter BLoC | `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/blocs/matching/` |\n| Card W
idget | `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/widgets/swipe_card.dart` |\n\n## 边界情况\
n\n1. **重复滑动**：同一用户短时间内重复滑动同一人，后端幂等处理（MySQL `INSERT 
IGNORE` 或唯一索引拦截）\n2. **滑动自己**：返回 `code=1000` 参数错误\n3. **缓存
击穿**：推荐池使用 Redis + 本地缓存双层防护，DB 查询加互斥锁\n4. **新用户冷启动*
*：注册完成后自动生成首批推荐池\n',
        message='Command executed successfully.',
